{"tid":544142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警察欠債】2017下半年37名警員無力還債　有人欠債長達12年","createTime":"2018-01-29T08:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T08:37:23.000Z","uid":5195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8086cb6a05f4625cf676237e7e47a80a71e9b323","tid":544142,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:30:02.000Z","msg":"保安局資料，警隊2017去年下半年有37名人員負債並無力償還。負債有多個原因，當中70.3%稱與家人親友問題有關，稱涉及「重要人生大事」及「揮霍」的分別有13.5%及10.8%，另外5.4%承認與「賭博」有關。在下半年錄得37名負債無力償還的警員中，其中有1人更是自2005年下半年起開始負債，至今長達12年；有2人是去年下半年度才開始負債。"},{"pid":"d0fc894ee07c9506eb8627b6201ea1895c0a9a56","tid":544142,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:36:01.000Z","msg":"作為全港最大嘅黑社會唔還都冇問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5761cdf299aaf0c622048cf6f87b0f89c7366d3","tid":544142,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0fc894ee07c9506eb8627b6201ea1895c0a9a56","tid":544142,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:36:01.000Z","msg":"作為全港最大嘅黑社會唔還都冇問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:37:23.000Z","msg":"反正破左產之後都唔駛扣人工還錢, <br />\n咁還黎做咩?"}]}